nodes.text: Dibbon Mallo was a Human male who lived during the time of the Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the resurgent Sith Empire. Kaliyo Djannis had a fling with Dibbon aboard Cipher Nine's X-70B Phantom-class prototype.
Dibbon Mallo first appeared in Star Wars: The Old Republic, a video game released by BioWare in 2011.
